show.title: I Fell For My Army Man
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: A wounded soldier. A doctor hiding a secret. Two undercover agents on opposite missions—tied together by fate. When Mohit Singh Bawa, a covert Special Forces agent, meets Dr. Prachi Sharma during a critical rescue, neither expects sparks to fly. But what begins as a medical emergency soon turns into a dangerous web of flirtation, suspicion, and unspoken truths. As hearts clash with hidden agendas and betrayal lurks in plain sight, the question remains— Is he her mission… or her greatest mistake?
